  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut the<strong> orange<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>in half, then cut 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]</span> orange into 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4] </span><strong>orange wedges</strong></p><p>Strip the <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from their stalks and chop the <strong>stalks</strong> finely, then roughly chop the <strong>leaves</strong> and keep separate</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) the <strong>garlic</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683103635827-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683103635827-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683103635827-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683103635827-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1683103635827-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the juice of the<strong> remaining orange halves </strong>(save the wedges for garnish!) to a small bowl with the <strong>ground cumin</strong>, <strong>dried</strong> <strong>oregano</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!),<strong> chopped coriander stalks </strong>(you'll use the leaves later!), <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and<strong> half </strong>the<strong> chopped garlic </strong>(save the rest for later!) </p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a very generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Mix until fully combined – this is your <strong>mojo-style marinade</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
