    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong></p><p>Deseed the <strong>sweet pointed pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>(scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Add the <strong>sliced</strong> <strong>red onion </strong>and <strong>sliced pepper</strong> to one side of a baking tray (or two!) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong>,<strong> </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p>",
