      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> white long grain rice</strong> to a pot with a lid with 175ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [350ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to very low and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until all the water has absorbed and the rice is cooked</p><p>Once done, remove from the heat, and set aside (lid on) to steam until serving</p>",
