    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut a large piece of <strong>tin foil </strong>and place the <strong>basa fillets</strong> in the centre of the foil</p><p>Pour the <strong>mojo-style marinade</strong> over the basa fillets, then scrunch the edges of the foil together around the fish to form a tightly sealed parcel</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 4? Make 2 separate parcels!</p>",
      "order": 5,
