    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained black beans</strong> to the cooked rice with <strong>half</strong> the <strong>chopped coriander leaves </strong>(save the rest for garnish!), the <strong>remaining chopped garlic</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong></p><p>Mix it all together and cook over a medium-low heat for 1-2 min or until warmed through – this is your <strong>black bean & coriander rice</strong></p>",
